Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's ultimatum under fire
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1bf
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 Feb 1980
President Carter's Olympic boycott threat over Soviet invasion comes under fire. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less